{"tid":2276083,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[AN/IOS/PC] Pixel Starships 寫AI 玩交易 對抗支那聯合艦隊","createTime":"2020-11-07T15:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T08:20:14.000Z","uid":170050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"805f1f03a9adcf1e9c2f51d5d18858abbe0a6f5b","tid":2276083,"uid":170050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pVus6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pVus6N.jpg&h=cabb25e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲簡介：<br />\n●像素為賣點嘅手遊<br />\n●多達25名角色<br />\n●自由搭建飛船，每間房間都有唔同功能<br />\n●全球服，有世界各地嘅玩家<br />\n●無體力限制，同玩家PVP為主<br />\n●有市場可以同其他玩家買賣，甚至手快搶人哋過貨<br />\n●合成系統，由2星到最強7星角色都有得合，有冇課金都玩到<br />\n●房間同角色都可以寫AI俾指令佢哋行動，複雜到可以寫論文，亦都可以手動<br />\n<br />\nAN：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.savysoda.pixelstarships\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.savysoda.pixelstarships&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=2ab083bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.savysoda.pixelstarships</a><br />\nIOS：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%9F%E8%89%A6-pixel-starships/id321756558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E5%2583%258F%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E6%2598%259F%25E8%2589%25A6-pixel-starships%2Fid321756558&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=7b66aa2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%9F%E8%89%A6-pixel-starships/id321756558</a><br />\nSteam：<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/378760/Pixel_Starships/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F378760%2FPixel_Starships%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=be399b7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/378760/Pixel_Starships/</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲介紹：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEervtz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEervtz.jpg&h=cf6d56bd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有勁多間房自由組砌，考慮自己戰術、船員走位、弱點房、維修等等，慢慢砌出自己獨特的星艦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6kFAqy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6kFAqy.jpg&h=76c5a303&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o5pbG5z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5pbG5z.jpg&h=9c036b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就算同一隻船員透過唔同訓練方法，都可以有唔同嘅定位，例如炮手、維修、坦克等，好似上面練血同攻擊力就作為反登艦，練科學數值，擺佢係盾室，盾室嘅reload time就會更快。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8i4Sq9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8i4Sq9F.jpg&h=c6cfdbf7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n公開嘅市場系統，透過遊戲三種資源礦、油同bux(=其他遊戲嘅鑽)嚟同人交易，但交易要收20%手續費，有時可以搶到人哋貪平用資源過嘅貴嘢，發達靠手速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xyvXp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xyvXp5.jpg&h=5ac701fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n每個角色都可以合成，最勁嘅7星角只可以合，唔似其他驚咁要不斷抽同一隻，少有Pay to Win情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMiPts3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMiPts3.jpg&h=d5b6e2ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHRp1N3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHRp1N3.jpg&h=c594b1b7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n寫AI俾指令房間攻擊唔同目標或者船員做嘢，好似上面喺一個維修AI，當自己房俾人攻擊緊時就會自動去維修到滿血，如果無其他人嚟幫手就企定定當坦吃傷。<br />\n<br />\n植入式招生文︰<br />\n我哋係Vega織女星，係聯合艦隊Radiance嘅其中一隊，主要係港澳台玩家嘅艦隊。<br />\n每月最後一星期都有聯賽，目前R隊對抗住支那嘅聯合艦隊Hydra龍，佢哋透過不良手法吞併同聯合其他艦隊主力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有好多外國玩家都不滿佢哋，組成聯合軍對抗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有興趣，加入嚟我哋一齊傾，有大量攻略教學文，想輕鬆玩或者認真玩都無任歡迎。<br />\nVega Discord：<a href=\"http://discord.gg/9qkpwVg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F9qkpwVg&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=8207e565\" target=\"_blank\">discord.gg/9qkpwVg</a><br />\n官方 Discord：<a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/Hwd9S2X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.com%2Finvite%2FHwd9S2X&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=1b2cc001\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.com/invite/Hwd9S2X</a><br />\n資料庫：<br />\n<a href=\"http://pixyship.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpixyship.com%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=6404e972\" target=\"_blank\">http://pixyship.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pixel-prestige.com/prestige-calculator.php?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpixel-prestige.com%2Fprestige-calculator.php%3F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=aec7867e\" target=\"_blank\">https://pixel-prestige.com/prestige-calculator.php?</a>"},{"pid":"88950f24b13793f7443d1433f2304d60cfc5caf0","tid":2276083,"uid":46739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"昌艦長, 你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0aingB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0aingB.png&h=20a1b3e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0675aa661978f743f2925e9e033a8c287af7c42a","tid":2276083,"uid":170050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你好 加嗰朋友呀"},{"pid":"c53db8426db9ef613b3f7a9a37bec03f9a9a9e85","tid":2276083,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"之前ea果陣有玩過下，最近無野做試下down返先"},{"pid":"ea713c2162fde40dd9984899a3473beeab874629","tid":2276083,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:01:23.000Z","msg":"見有中文玩吓先<br />\n<br />\nd任務怪都打唔贏<img 